{"word":"G795 - ἀστοχέω - astochéō - as-tokh-eh'-o - Err","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀστοχέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">astochéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">as-tokh-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Err</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விலகிப்போ, வழுவிப்போ, விலகு"},{"paragraph":"to deviate from"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <b>&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03B9;&#x03C7;&#x03BF;&#x03C2;</b> <b>stoichos</b> (an <i>aim</i>); to <i>miss</i> the mark, that is, (figuratively) <i>deviate</i> from truth: - err, swerve.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}